程序包 cn.inbot.navigationlib.event

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    OnActionStatusChangedEvent
    Navigation action status changed event.
    OnBuildMapInfoChangedEvent
    Build map information changed event.
    OnCruiseInfoChangedEvent
    Cruise information changed event.
    OnInquiryRelocateEvent
    Inquiry relocate event 充电时重定位事件类 This event will be posted when the robot is charging and the current position of the robot is far away from the charging point.
    OnLocateInfoChangedEvent
    Locate information changed event 定位事件类 This event will be posted when the robot's locate information changed.
    OnMapInfoUpdatedEvent
    Map info updated event 地图信息事件类 This event will be posted when the robot's map information updated.
    OnNavigateInfoChangedEvent
    Navigation info changed event 导航信息事件类 This event will be posted when the robot's navigation information changed.
    OnNavigationClientConnectedEvent
    Navigation client connected event 连接导航事件类 This event will be posted when you connected to the remote navigation client.
    OnNavigationClientDisconnectedEvent
    Navigation client disconnected event 与导航断开连接事件类 This event will be posted when you disconnected to the remote navigation client.
    OnNavigationInitedEvent
    Navigation inited event 导航初始化事件类 This event will be posted when the remote navigation client is inited.
    OnOperateNavigationPageEvent
    Operate navigation page event 操作导航页面事件类 This event will be posted when the user touch the navigation page.
    OnReceiveNavigatePathDataEvent
    Receive navigation path data event 接收导航路径事件类 This event will be posted after receiving the navigation path data when navigating.
    OnReceiveNavigationDiganoseResultEvent
    Created by shisenkun on 2020/12/10.
    OnReceiveRobotPositionEvent
    Receive robot position event.
    OnRequestCloseEntranceEvent
    Request close entrance event 请求关闭门禁事件类 This event will be posted when the robot requests to close the entrance device.
    OnRequestOpenEntranceEvent
    Request open entrance event 请求打开门禁事件类 This event will be posted when the robot requests to open the entrance device.
    OnRobotBasicStatusChangedEvent
    Robot's basic status changed event.
    OnRobotBlockedEvent
    机器人受阻事件 机器人在执行巡航任务时，在很多种情况下会卡在半路，例如：因梯控问题导致等电梯多次持续超时、去目标点长时间获取不到路径等等 遇到这种情况，需要上报给上层应用，上层应用再去做处理（例如发短信提醒）
    OnSwitchMapCallbackEvent
    Switch map result callback event。
